{
  "stem": "15732.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think-- I think that we found out that after the Germans left.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think we found that out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was afterwards that we found out that there was a-- an order by the Germans that the Romanians did not obey.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] The Russians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the unit that liberated us was a unit from Middle East-- Middle Asia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were [NON-ENGLISH], they were called.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Very tiny, tiny soldiers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were lying on the-- afterwards they were lying in the-- in the town hall of the place, and sleeping on the floor, dirty and rumpled.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we thought, what a wonderful miracle of God is that, that those soldiers defeated those organized Germans [LAUGHS] that were so-- so organized, they were sitting on those motorbikes, that you could think that-- that they are really [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were defeated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At that time, we thought it must be a sign of God, that God was on the right side this time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They saw-- they were on advance from middle Russia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They went through the whole of the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the whole of Ukraine was burnt out and devastated by the Germans in their retreat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when they arrived in Cernauti at Cernauti, we still had houses standing and there was still, so to speak, a city that was not destroyed, it was a miracle for them.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a miracle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were very nice to us, in their way, very detached.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But nice to us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were preoccupied with their war, with their problems.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They liberated us, they went further, and then came the Russian administration.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then that started the normal life being organized.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
